inputs.text: In an abandoned, overgrown castle hall, a young sorceress summons mystical, fiery energy from the depths of her staff. Her dark dress ripples as the flames swirl around her, igniting her surroundings. Broken statues and old stone walls are consumed by the heat, while ethereal tendrils of fire wrap around her figure. The magic she wields could either save or doom the forgotten ruins as ancient power surges through her.
